<paragraph blockId="30.[151,1436,1353,1738]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,255,1389,1414]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">Note</emphasis>
: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez &amp; Engel" authorityYear="2012" box="[272,440,1389,1414]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riyadhensis">
<emphasis box="[272,440,1389,1414]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. riyadhensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is likely conspecific with 
<taxonomicName authority="Cockerell 1937" authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1937" box="[746,1123,1389,1414]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodoleucura">
<emphasis box="[746,937,1389,1414]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. rhodoleucura</emphasis>
Cockerell 1937
</taxonomicName>
, described from 
<collectingCountry box="[1316,1436,1389,1414]" name="Zimbabwe" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">Zimbabwe</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Praz, C. J." box="[158,285,1426,1450]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" pagination="1 - 54" refId="ref48342" refString="Praz, C. J. (2017) Subgeneric classification and biology of the leafcutter and dauber bees (genus Megachile Latreille) of the western Palearctic (Hymenoptera, Apoidea, Megachilidae). Journal of Hymenoptera Research, 55, 1 - 54. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / jhr. 55.11255" type="journal article" year="2017">Praz 2017</bibRefCitation>
). The female 
<typeStatus box="[459,557,1425,1450]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1937" box="[609,806,1425,1450]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodoleucura">
<emphasis box="[609,806,1425,1450]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. rhodoleucura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is sculpturally identical with 
<taxonomicName authority="(Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel, 2012)" authorityName="Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riyadhensis">
<emphasis box="[1174,1436,1425,1450]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">Megachile riyadhensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Alqarni, A. S. &amp; Hannan, M. A. &amp; Gonzalez, V. H. &amp; Engel, M. S." box="[158,658,1461,1486]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" pagination="71 - 83" refId="ref46135" refString="Alqarni, A. S. Hannan, M. A., Gonzalez, V. H. &amp; Engel, M. S. (2012) A new species of Chalicodoma from Saudi Arabia with modified facial setae (Hymenoptera, Megachilidae). ZooKeys, 204, 71 - 83. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 204.3228" type="journal article" year="2012">Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel, 2012</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and differs from that species only in the coloration of the metasomal vestiture (it is fulvous in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1937" box="[433,623,1497,1522]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodoleucura">
<emphasis box="[433,623,1497,1522]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. rhodoleucura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and snow white in 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[843,1009,1497,1522]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riyadhensis">
<emphasis box="[843,1009,1497,1522]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. riyadhensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). We follow 
<bibRefCitation author="Praz, C. J." box="[1157,1289,1498,1522]" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" pagination="1 - 54" refId="ref48342" refString="Praz, C. J. (2017) Subgeneric classification and biology of the leafcutter and dauber bees (genus Megachile Latreille) of the western Palearctic (Hymenoptera, Apoidea, Megachilidae). Journal of Hymenoptera Research, 55, 1 - 54. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / jhr. 55.11255" type="journal article" year="2017">Praz (2017)</bibRefCitation>
in refraining from putting 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Alqarni, Hannan, Gonzalez and Engel" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[299,465,1533,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riyadhensis">
<emphasis box="[299,465,1533,1558]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. riyadhensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1937" box="[681,870,1533,1558]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="281" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhodoleucura">
<emphasis box="[681,870,1533,1558]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="281">M. rhodoleucura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
until the male of the latter is known.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
